Feature: Hotel Booking In Adactin Application

Scenario: 1 User login In Adactin  Application

Given user Launch the web application
When user Enter the Username in user user field
And  user Enter the password in password field 
Then user clik the login button to navigate to sear hotel page


Scenario: 2 User search for hotel with the required details

When User Select the location from the dropdown
And  User Select the Hotel from the dropdown
And  User Select the Room Type from the dropdown
And  User Select the number of Rooms form the dropdown
And  User need to provide the check In date from the Calander 
And  User need to provide the check Out date from the Calander
And  User Select the Adults per room from the dropdown
And  User Select the Child per room from the dropdown
Then User Click the secrch button to find hotel 

